Requirements: 
  
  apache (or rewrite .htaccess appropriately for whatever webserver you want.) 

  mongodb-server

  php inc mongodbclient 
    pear install -f pecl/mongo
    
  a desire to use a docstore that is usable within 5 minutes, 100% flexible yet still allows for conventional mvc code when you need it. 

See the wiki for installation and use 
